  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2950910/" class="title-link">勿忘历史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2950910"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/8405571/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/8405571/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">懂你</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-23"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-23 18:54:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2950910_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在大多数人心中，蒋介石和国民党总是反动顽固的，其实不然，作为炎黄子孙，蒋介石这个刽子手面对民族大义也是不含糊的的，看了就知道

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2950910_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2950910_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





